#: ../../../release/dev/install-exit-code-fidelity.rst:2
msgid "install-exit-code-fidelity"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/dev/install-exit-code-fidelity.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :option:`cmake --install` command now reports a non-zero exit code when "
"an install script fails.  Previously, a parallel install (enabled by the :"
"prop_gbl:`INSTALL_PARALLEL` global property) always reported success, and a "
"serial install could lose the failure of an earlier component that exited "
"via :command:`cmake_language(EXIT) <cmake_language>` when a later component "
"succeeded."
msgstr ""
